Name: AcceptedRxhubConsent
Support Remarks: Enable this Item key to enable transmission of prescription data for RxHub activity report.

Name: AccessReportView
Support Remarks: Set value to "Yes" to VIEW user-defined MS Access reports only - Enables EMR Access Log Report under the Reports tab. This report gives a log based on date range/per patient/per user/per staff.

Name: AccountsLookup_MaxDays
Support Remarks: File > Practice Defaults > Performance tab > Accounts Lookup. When enabled, this Item Key displays a warning message if the service dates difference is more than the number of days specified in this field.
UI Controlled: Yes - File > Settings > Practice Defaults > Performance tab.
